#* '''1985''', David H. Rothman, ''The Silicon Jungle'', New York: Ballantine, Chapter 10, p.{{nbsp}}171,<sup>[https://www.gutenberg.org/files/54360/54360-h/54360-h.htm]</sup>
#*: With actorlike polish he '''intonated''' through the third page {{...}}
# {{lb|en|transitive|dated}} To [[say]] or [[speak]] with a certain [[intonation]].
#* '''1845''', {{w|Sheridan Le Fanu}}, ''The Cock and the Anchor'', Dublin: William Curry, Jun., Volume 1, Chapter 6, p.{{nbsp}}74,<sup>[https://archive.org/details/cockanchorbeingc01lefa]</sup>
