#* '''1844''', ''The order for morning and evening prayer, and the Litany : with plain-tune, according to the use of the United Church of England and Ireland'', London: J. Burns,Editor’s Preface,<sup>[https://catalog.hathitrust.org/Record/100242021]</sup>
#*: A comma or colon was '''intonated''' by the fall of a minor third from the key-note on the ultimate or penultimate and ultimate syllables of the clause {{...}}
